    <footer>
        <p>© 2026 Iron Pulse Fitness Center. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        <p>123 Performance Way, New York, NY • Mon-Sun: 5:00 AM - 11:00 PM</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
